            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Remembered for good and for blessing (they) who maintained and made this … in the
                    second eyar of the Sabbatical in the fourth thousand … hundred and … year since
                    the world was created … in it. May there be peace.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>Dated synagogue inscriptions are very rare, so it is unfortunate the precise year
                    does not survive.</p>
            </div>
